---
/**
 * rest-api/0009 · Figure 2 — "route the failure to the right code": 400 for
 * malformed syntax, 422 for parsed-but-invalid, 409 for a state conflict, and
 * never tunnel any of these through 200.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from docs/rest-api/lessons/0009-error-design-rate-limiting-observability.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an .astro component for the
 * kebab-case-SVG reason. No arrowhead markers here, so no local <defs> is needed.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 600 150"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Routing an error to a status code: 400 for malformed syntax, 422 for valid syntax but invalid data, 409 for a state conflict; never 200"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="300"
                y="16"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">ROUTE THE FAILURE TO THE RIGHT CODE</text
            >
            <rect x="8" y="34" width="180" height="70" rx="9" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"
            ></rect>
            <text x="98" y="58" text-anchor="middle" font-size="16" font-weight="700" fill="#9a2417"
                >400</text
            >
            <text x="98" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#7a2218"
                >malformed syntax</text
            >
            <text x="98" y="91" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >server can't even parse it</text
            >
            <rect x="208" y="34" width="180" height="70" rx="9" fill="#fbfaf2" stroke="#7a1f12"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="298"
                y="58"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="16"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">422</text
            >
            <text x="298" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#2c2a26"
                >parsed, but invalid</text
            >
            <text x="298" y="91" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >semantic / validation fail</text
            >
            <rect x="408" y="34" width="184" height="70" rx="9" fill="#eef2f5" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="500"
                y="58"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="16"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">409</text
            >
            <text x="500" y="76" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#1f3a5a"
                >state conflict</text
            >
            <text x="500" y="91" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >collides with current state</text
            >
            <text x="300" y="128" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >✗ Don't tunnel any of these through <tspan
                    font-family="ui-monospace,monospace"
                    font-weight="700">200</tspan
                > — the status line IS the contract.</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        <code>400</code> malformed · <code>422</code> well-formed-but-invalid · <code>409</code> conflict.
        Same body shape, honest status line.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
